result.notes:
Two surveys of Cape Bank rMCZ site have been completed to date (Apr 2015):

Cruise: Cefas_cend2514

Date: 15-11-2014 - 19-12-2014

Data collected:

MB Bathymetry Coverage (Contractor): 100% (CHP) - Data reprocessed Aug 14. 
Data being processed (Cefas_cend2514 & Cefas_cend0115) by 31/3/15

MB Backscatter Coverage (Contractor): 100% (CHP) - Data reprocessed Aug 14. 
Data being processed (Cefas_cend2514 & Cefas_cend0115) by 31/3/15

SS Coverage: None acquired to Date

Video and Stills Samples to date: 106 video transects; 1298 stills 
(Cefas_cend2514 & Cefas_cend0115) - to be processed by 31/3/15

PSA Samples to date: 26 (Cefas_cend2514 & Cefas_cefas0115) - to be processed 
by 31/3/15

Infauna Samples to date: 26 (Cefas_cend2514 & Cefas_cefas0115) - to be 
processed by 31/3/15
